UID:a4e2b7770722477c29b995a4f0412be7@events.in.gov
DESCRIPTION:Join the Brown County Rock and Mineral Club at the Nature Cent
 er&nbsp\; as we take a look at some amazing rock displays and learn more a
 bout why geology rocks! This event wil run from 11am-4pm in the shelter ho
 use at the Nature Center and will feature crafts for kids. There will be G
 old Panning\, Rock Painting\, Geodes\, Fossils\, Minerals\, and more! Prog
 ram schedule TBA.
LOCATION:Brown County State Park\, Nature Center\, 1405 S.R. 46 W\, Nashvi
 lle\, IN 
